title: Haunted Tomb of the Blind Lady
story: After the defeat of the Blind Lady the tomb has changed hands many times. Now it is controlled by a band of pirates.

notes.text: A notable double door on the southern wall of the large room.
A carpet of force in the middle of a circle of runes on the ground.
A writing on the wall: DWARFS UNITE!
A crate holds a strange, whispering ring.
